 📉 Customer Churn Prediction App

This project is a Machine Learning web application* built using "Streamlit" that predicts whether a customer will churn based on their service usage and account information. The model was trained using "Logistic Regression" with the help of the `scikit-learn` library.

---

🚀 Features

- Upload your own customer dataset (CSV)
- Predict churn outcomes using a pre-trained model
- Clean and interactive user interface built with Streamlit
- Data preprocessing and visualization (optional)

---

 🧠 Model Used

- *ogistic Regression** from `scikit-learn`
- Trained on a telecom customer churn dataset
- Feature engineering and preprocessing included

